sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User
    participant UI as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant BE as Backend (Express)
    participant DB as SQLite DB
    participant ASAPI as Agent-service-api (poller)
    participant AS as Agent-service (FastAPI / CrewAI)

    User->>UI: Configure conversation + agent\nClick Execute
    UI->>BE: Create execution job (conversation_id)
    BE->>DB: Insert job (queued)
    BE-->>UI: Return job id

    loop Job status updates
        UI->>BE: Fetch job status
        BE->>DB: Read job row
        BE-->>UI: status/progress + session link (when available)
    end

    loop Poll for work
        ASAPI->>BE: Claim next queued job
        BE->>DB: Mark job claimed/running
        BE-->>ASAPI: Job payload + conversation script
    end

    ASAPI->>AS: Execute conversation turn-by-turn
    AS-->>ASAPI: Replies + tool calls + metadata

    ASAPI->>BE: Post session + transcript
    BE->>DB: Persist session + session_messages
    BE->>DB: Mark job completed + session_id
    BE-->>ASAPI: OK

    UI->>BE: Fetch session transcript
    BE->>DB: Read execution_session + session_messages
    BE-->>UI: Transcript + metrics
    UI-->>User: Render session viewer
